<lb n="0499a13" ed="T"/>六</note>　陀呵陀呵<note place="inline">十七</note>　鉢遮鉢遮<note place="inline">十八</note>　祁利祁利<note place="inline">十九</note>
<lb n="0499a14" ed="T"/>　醯那醯那<note place="inline">二十</note>　<note n="0499002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">求＝末【元】【明】</note><note n="0499002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求【大】，末【元】【明】</note><app n="0499002"><lem wit="【大】">求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】 【明】">末</rdg></app>利陀<note place="inline">二十一</note>　末利陀<note place="inline">二十二</note>　鉢囉末
<lb n="0499a15" ed="T"/>利<note place="inline">二十三</note>」</p>
<lb n="0499a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0499a1601">「彌勒菩薩告勅，令除一切雨障莎呵。」又說呪曰：</p>
<lb n="0499a17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0499a1701">「佛提佛提<note place="inline">一</note>　浮佛提浮佛提<note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0499a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0499a1801">「令諸眾生持佛功德，除滅一切障業重罪。」而
<lb n="0499a19" ed="T"/>說呪曰：</p>
<lb n="0499a20" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0499a2001">「陀羅尼<note place="inline">一</note>　馱離<note place="inline">二</note>　輸婆摩帝<note place="inline">三</note>　求那伽囉鉢囉
<lb n="0499a21" ed="T"/>鉢泥<note place="inline">四</note>　摩呵若奴盧枳<note place="inline">去聲</note><note place="inline">五</note>　輸說羅<note place="inline">引</note>達彌<note place="inline">六</note>
